OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMainly fine, with some warm
OL,6,Fsunny spells and light winds, although
OL,7,Fcloud amounts generally increasing
OL,8,Fwith rain and showers spreading
OL,9,Fnorthwards. Possible rumble of thunder
OL,10,Fin the southeast by mid-afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloudier overnight as band of
OL,13,Frain, occasionally heavy, moves
OL,14,Fnorthwards through the region, this
OL,15,Fclears from the south by the morning.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FA dry start becoming cloudy
OL,18,Fwith showers develop during the
OL,19,Fafternoon, some of which could be
OL,20,Fheavy at times. A breezy southeasterly
OL,21,Fwind will veer northwesterly later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
